{"tid":1783881,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得一邊扮黃一邊賣支那化學零食好嘔心","createTime":"2019-12-15T08:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T13:59:12.000Z","uid":216720,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0baef0958b21ac930a9de4b3a8a590221dd4a805","tid":1783881,"uid":216720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得有唔少舖頭都鍾意扮黃，賣人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都留意左呢間嘢一排，我以為過一排會有人發現，<br />\n但過左半年都冇人講，反而多左客。<br />\n終於忍唔住要開個post講下！<br />\n<br />\n呢間舖頭由反送中開始，佢都一直有share啲post出黎，<br />\n又話罷工，又話政府警察點點點⋯⋯<br />\n但到要遊行既時候就自己走去遊行story打卡，舖頭就繼續開。呢頭開完post話遊行緊，下一個post就話有新貨返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n番咩貨？咪啲大陸淘寶化學嘢囉⋯⋯<br />\n啲辣條，化學邊爐等等啦，店入面七成都係大陸嘢黎，幫襯佢同番大陸消費冇乜分別。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近仲整埋啲咩連儂板比人貼下嘢，咁又呃到一班妹豬幫襯，啲人又真系覺得冇問題㗎wo！我明依家生意難做，你唔出聲我都覺得算啦，但可唔可以唔好借啲位加入黃色經濟圈？紅扮紅好核突啊大佬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一係你就唔好賣大陸嘢食啦⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n如果大家去旺中，又口痕，不如幫襯番啲真正有貼紙既黃店！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oBsmfHS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoBsmfHS.png&h=85350acf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xTOHKBe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxTOHKBe.png&h=186fe570&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YE6upBi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYE6upBi.png&h=bc34d27f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxZWO24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxZWO24.png&h=1acb7f69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R0hhyuM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0hhyuM.png&h=2f86cca6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16822104a017332c11fe7403660580a32625a9a1","tid":1783881,"uid":163704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15